MusicBrainz::Client version 0.01
================================

This module provides access to the libmusicbrainz client library from
perl.

For more information about the Music Brainz project visit the projects
website at http://www.musicbrainz.org/


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

or alternatively using CPAN.pm

   perl -MCPAN -e 'install MusicBrainz::Client'


DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

   MusicBrainz::Queries 0.01 or later 
   libmusicbrainz 2.0 or later from http://www.musicbrainz.org/
   perl 5.6.1 or later


